OL,3,CBen Condon baby inquest finds serious
OL,4,Chospital failings after 10-year
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FAn inquest in 2016 recorded Ben's
OL,8,Fcause of death as two acute
OL,9,Frespiratory illnesses and prematurity,
OL,10,Fbut the High Court quashed the verdict
OL,11,Fafter new evidence emerged, following
OL,12,Fa 10-year campaign by Ben's parents.
OL,14,FAt the conclusion of the second
OL,15,Finquest into his death on Friday,
OL,16,FRobert Sowersby, assistant coroner for
OL,17,FAvon, reached several damning
OL,18,Fconclusions about the care Ben
OL,19,Freceived and found that the bacterial
OL,20,Finfection had been a cause of his
OL,21,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
