OL,7,FMr Sowersby recorded a new cause of
OL,8,Fdeath as acute respiratory distress
OL,9,Fsyndrome (ARDS), pseudomonas bacterial
OL,10,Finfection, metapneumovirus (hMPV) and
OL,11,Fprematurity.
OL,13,FHe criticised the "patronising"
OL,14,Fapproach of Bristol Children's
OL,15,FHospital towards Ben's parents but
OL,16,Fsaid a coroner's court was not able to
OL,17,Faddress concerns about the swabs.
