OL,7,FProfessor Stuart Walker, the managing
OL,8,Fdirector of University Hospitals
OL,9,FBristol and Weston NHS Foundation
OL,10,FTrust, told the inquest there is no
OL,11,Fevidence that post-mortem samples were
OL,12,Ftaken from Ben Condon after his death.
OL,14,FSpeaking after the conclusion, Ben's
OL,15,Fparents said: "As a family we have
OL,16,Fbeen silenced, stonewalled and
OL,17,Fgaslighted by University Hospital
OL,18,FBristol and Weston Trust. The trauma
OL,19,Fwe have faced as a result of their
OL,20,Fconduct is indescribable.
OL,26,@wD@OOU
