OL,7,F"We are grateful that the trust stands
OL,8,Fby their position that their failure
OL,9,Fto prescribe earlier antibiotics
OL,10,Fcontributed to Ben's death and that on
OL,11,Fthe balance of probabilities, had they
OL,12,Ftreated him with antibiotics earlier,
OL,13,Fhe would have survived.
OL,15,F"Today, the coroner has included the
OL,16,Fpseudomonas bacterial infection and
OL,17,Fthe impact of surfactant on Ben's
OL,18,Fcause of death, which is all we ever
OL,19,Fwanted and everything we have fought
OL,20,Ffor."
