OL,7,FIn a statement issued following the
OL,8,Finquest, Professor Stuart Walker said
OL,9,Fthe trust was "deeply sorry" that Ben
OL,10,Fdied while in its care and for how it
OL,11,Fcommunicated with his family after his
OL,12,Fdeath.
OL,14,F"We have undertaken significant
OL,15,Flearning and reflection in the 10
OL,16,Fyears since then," Prof Walker said.
OL,18,F"We accept the conclusion of the
OL,19,Fassistant coroner, and I would again
OL,20,Flike to acknowledge the distress
OL,21,Fexperienced by Ben's family."
