OL,7,FBorn in February 2015 at 29 weeks, Ben
OL,8,Fspent seven weeks in the neonatal
OL,9,Fintensive care unit at Southmead
OL,10,FHospital before being discharged on 7
OL,11,FApril.
OL,13,FThree days after being taken home, he
OL,14,Fbecame unwell following cold-like
OL,15,Fsymptoms and his parents took him to
OL,16,FWeston General Hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
