OL,7,FHe was transferred to Bristol
OL,8,FChildren's Hospital the following day,
OL,9,Fwhere he was diagnosed with Human
OL,10,FMetapneumovirus (hMPV) and later found
OL,11,Fto have acute respiratory distress
OL,12,Fsyndrome (ARDS).
OL,14,FHe died following a cardiac arrest on
OL,15,F17 April 2015.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
