OL,3,CBen Condon baby inquest finds serious
OL,4,Chospital failings after 10-year
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FAn inquest in June 2016 recorded Ben's
OL,8,Fcause of death as acute respiratory
OL,9,Fdistress syndrome (ARDS),
OL,10,Fmetapneumovirus (hMPV) and
OL,11,Fprematurity, and found giving
OL,12,Fantibiotics would not have prevented
OL,13,Fit.
OL,15,FHowever, in 2017, University Hospitals
OL,16,FBristol and Weston NHS Foundation
OL,17,FTrust admitted a failure to give Ben
OL,18,Ftimely antibiotics had contributed to
OL,19,Fhis death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
