OL,7,FThe High Court quashed the original
OL,8,Fverdict in 2021 and ordered a fresh
OL,9,Finquest, following a decade-long
OL,10,Fcampaign by Ben's parents.
OL,12,FBen's parents said over the past 10
OL,13,Fyears, the trust has treated them with
OL,14,F"complete disrespect".
OL,16,FJenny Condon, Ben's mother, said: "All
OL,17,FI wanted is to find out how Ben
OL,18,Factually died and have a correct death
OL,19,Fcertificate, but it's felt like there
OL,20,Fhas been a massive inequality in the
OL,21,Fwhole situation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
