OL,7,F"A feeling of, you're never going to
OL,8,Fbe able to get anything from it
OL,9,Fbecause you're just going to get shut
OL,10,Fdown. It was intimidating, to say the
OL,11,Fleast.
OL,13,FThe 43-year-old, from Weston-super-
OL,14,FMare, added: "They know my grief, they
OL,15,Fknow the damage they've caused, and
OL,16,Fyet they're still carrying on.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
