OL,7,F"I'm in a situation where I'm having
OL,8,Fto relive that day again and again,
OL,9,Flistening to every single day for the
OL,10,Fpast three weeks. Especially the final
OL,11,Fmoments. And yet there is still no
OL,12,Fcompassion".
OL,14,FBen's father, Allyn Condon has accused
OL,15,Fthe hospital of "covering up" the
OL,16,Ffailings that led to his son's death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
