OL,7,F"Every failure we've discovered, we
OL,8,Fdiscovered ourselves," he said.
OL,9,F"Everything that has ever been
OL,10,Fadmitted is because we found it.
OL,11,FEverything we've got we've had to
OL,12,Ffight for".
OL,14,FThe Condon family said that they had
OL,15,Fhoped the hearing "would bring an end
OL,16,Fto all our unanswered questions" and
OL,17,Fenable them to begin rebuilding their
OL,18,Flives.
