OL,7,FHowever, during the inquest a document
OL,8,Fappeared to suggest that four swabs
OL,9,Fwere taken from Ben's body and sent
OL,10,Ffor tests on April 18 and 19.
OL,12,FThis was despite Ben's parents being
OL,13,Fassured that there was no need for
OL,14,Ftheir baby to undergo a post-mortem
OL,15,Fexamination, leading to his body being
OL,16,Fcremated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
