OL,7,FThey added: "We will be contacting the
OL,8,FGeneral Medical Council and the Human
OL,9,FTissue Authority to trigger the
OL,10,Fprocess for a potential criminal
OL,11,Finvestigation under the Human Tissue
OL,12,FAct 2004."
OL,14,F"We will continue to fight until we
OL,15,Fare sure no other family will have to
OL,16,Fface the irreparable pain and
OL,17,Fsuffering we have had, and are still
OL,18,Fhaving, to endure."
